title: The Bradys Go Bowling (The Brady Bunch)
description: One of the earliest (and truest)forms of reality television took place on a sound stage in Los Angeles where two teams competed against each other to win prizes for people in the studio. It's a 'game show' crossed with 'reality television' and no matter what you call it, it's hysterical! What made the two shows on this DVD particularly unique is they pitted members of the Brady Bunch against each other and against 2 of the kids from `The Waltons`.
